Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dark lord of riches is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan will chase him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pay your rent!
Comment: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our father disappeared after accumulating gambling debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we were left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:18.46,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,The soft feeling of a futon that has been aired out in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:23.40,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,It's flat like a rice cracker but ever so fluff{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:31.56,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,As usual, my younger sister is busily preparing a delicious dinne{\fsp-1}r.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.70,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I like this natural routine more than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.07,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.03,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:49.78,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Today at 7:30 p.m., the dark lord of riches will make his monthly visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don’t worr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m fine, I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we pay this month’s rent, the next month will be hard on us.{SHOESTRING BUDGET}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the landlord won’t give us a break, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:31.87,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,When we eat dinne{\fsp-1}r,{\fsp0.5} we try to avoid the subject of mone{\fsp-1}{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.18,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,This has been our unwritten rule for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:38.04,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,But today is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, today I will protect you from the scary demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, Asu. Onee-chan will try her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He’s coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:58.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn’t come...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean this month’s rent payment is canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don’t think it’s that simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must not be collecting the rent this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you’re certainly in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, the landlord must have decided to not collect the rent anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s why I’m feeling so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably won the lottery or something, so he doesn’t need to collect rent anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s why he didn’t come by last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we won’t have to pay the rent ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don’t think things will go that well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m wearing my swimsuit under my t-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, it doesn’t matter how soaked I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should go change too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t do that, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, it’s fine, as long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so relieved when that annoying landlord didn’t come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was such a relief not having to pay rent this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The landlord didn’t come by last night saying, “Pay the rent!” right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have won the lottery—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, the landlord is in the hospital right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He’s hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that he fell from somewhere and broke his leg or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn’t even tell anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even if someone visited him, he’d just brush them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess it can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only has himself to blame for his attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must be lonel{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, with no one visiting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he didn’t win a lotter{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, and the rent’s not canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course that wouldn’t happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m pretty stupid, aren’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s what I like about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Onee-chan, you really believed your own explanation, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, why don’t we go visit the landlord together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it a little frightening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I’m a little bit afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a dark lord after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he realizes that we’ve only brought one apple...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(25,358,\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,450)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(-15,318,\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,425)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(-55,278,\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,385)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(-95,238,\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,335)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(-145,188,\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,280)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(-185,148,\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,220)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(-225,108,\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,157)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(-265,68,\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,97)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(-305,28\alpha&HE0)\pos(356,37)}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He’ll probably scold us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we don’t have enough money to buy anything more expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it’s better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probabl{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}. Landlord! We’ve come to visit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Idiots!{tsundere~}{<+Isurugi_Mio> kick the bitch in the teeth <+Isurugi_Mio> j-j-j-jam it in <+Isurugi_Mio> and then he’ll go all deredere}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reall{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a hospital, so don’t speak so loudl{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn’t the landlord using a loud vo—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, um, your leg. Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it look okay to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do all these examinations, and smoking’s prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you start slicing that apple already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just put it on the side for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was pretty hot this morning, so I watered the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren’t watering the yard, you were playing in the wate{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Um, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wore a swimsuit under my t-shirt, so it’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was asking if you played with the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, we’ll be going now.
Comment: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I AM GRUNTING
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we expected, that was pretty scar{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he ate the apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For tonight’s dinne{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}, does burdock salad and seaweed scrambled eggs sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I’ll look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, go brush your teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, I’m going to visit the landlord again today after school.
Comment: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, {\alpha&HFF&}I’m going to visit the landlord again today after school.
Comment: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, I’m going to visit the landlord again today after school. {lol it looks bad}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I might be home late, so don’t worr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought about it, and it’s just like what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone who was hospitalized and had no visitors would feel lonel{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was me, I’d feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I think I’ll go visit him more for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that’s a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,854)}You don’t have to force yourself to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, Mrs. Yaoichi asked me to give this watermelon to the landlord.{I don’t hear her saying suika (watermelon) anywhere in this sentence, but perhaps it’s implied. Regardless, I think that given the following sentence, this translation makes more "sense"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you’re going to visit him every da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, then I will too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait. I-It hurts, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, it seems like he’s still in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the?! You two came again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Mrs. Yaoichi asked Asu to bring this watermelon as a gift.{八百屋 【やおや】 (n) greengrocer;}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it’s a little small, the skin’s firm, so it must be delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll go cut it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can eat it whenever you get hungr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}. Landlord, would you like some barley tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought it from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s pretty hot toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, so why don’t you cool off with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for delivering the watermelon, Asu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man didn’t eat it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t mind him, he’s always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, these are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my thanks for making that deliver{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s meat, so eat a lot and cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing! We have quite a feast today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! She really gave us a lot of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.59,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’m truly fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.64,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,No matter how depressed I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:20.81,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,as long as I get to eat dinner with Asu like this,\Nthose feelings will float away like a cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:23.52,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow I’ll be able to smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:29.75,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Then I’ll definitely be able to have the energy to try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.91,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I wonder how the landlord is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:38.54,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Maybe this man who lives alone really doesn’t have anyone like we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:43.57,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Asu probably saw that in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, why don’t we visit him every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let’s do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you two visit a lot, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be hard to come by every da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is M{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}. Landlord still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m not sure. He was awake a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the, it’s you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}. Landlord, I picked some flowers for you toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu picked them from the roadside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys don’t have to come anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said you guys don’t have to come anymore.{definitely tsundere}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we troubled him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, we have to prepare for the leaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu! Go get the dishes and pans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? It’s not leaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did someone fix it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:06.44,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,{\t(3210,3385,\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}I heard that he fell from somewhere and broke his leg or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:17.57,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,All the time, the landlord’s expression never changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.03,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Even when Asu was massaging his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:24.63,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,or when I tried to get him to say “Ah” while feeding him pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.23,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,His face always had a lonely look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:30.98,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,But I have a feeling that he was never annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(1936,2895,\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}It must be hard to come by every da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! That’s why he said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.81,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,You guys don’t have to come anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him fixing himself up as we came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was afraid he would hate me for showing up every da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn’t know what I would do if he ended up hating you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}. Landlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-what? Didn’t I tell you guys not to come anymore?{tsun tsun}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our last visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please get well soon, and come back to the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.{dere dere}{SERIOUSLY}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:57.63,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Today I’m wearing my swimsuit under my t-shirt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:03.05,dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,But on a hot day like this, swimming is still\Ndefinitely better than just playing with wate{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn’t a pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn’t this a washbasin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t mind, don’t mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it great to have a pool in the yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can also wash your hair while we’re at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We’ll be scolded by the landlord again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’ll be fine because we’re good friends with the landlord now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who said we’re good friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, M{\fsp-1}r{\fsp0.5}. Landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this mess. What were you guys thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, what should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t sa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp0.5}, “What should I do?!”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pay the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, the landlord still collected this month’s rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after that, he quietly said, “Thank you for watering the flowers{\fsp-2}”{\fsp}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
